Package: naiver
Type: Package
Title: A simple Naïve Bayesian Classifier for biological sequences and other texts

Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mikołaj", "Charchuta", , "mmcharchuta@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1403-4020"))
Description:
    Package for classification based analysis of sequences. As an example, it 
    implements the naïve bayesian classifier from the Ribosomal Database 
    Project. We will likely include  other methods of classifcation and possibly
    some methods of visualizing the data.
